Package: espn.com
Title: ESPN Public Sports API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the ESPN public sports API. Get scores, standings, and team info for NFL, NBA, MLB, NHL, and soccer. Includes LLM context injection via espn_context().
